      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="8881st">8881st meeting</inline>, on <docDate date="2021-10-15" refersTo="#adoptionDate">15 October 2021</docDate></docTitle>
